summaries.short: Season Three Premiere. Fresh off his college tour, Pete takes a young aspiring comedian under his wing as he returns to NYC.
summaries.full: Season Three Premiere. As his successful two-month college comedy tour comes to an end, Pete, donning a new look and confidence to match, takes a college-aged aspiring comedian, Jaboukie, under his wing. But Pete's return to New York finds him having an awkward reunion and a big audition at the Comedy Cellar that could change everything.
